page.title: 10CUTTESLOWE PARK
page.content: Cutteslowe Park takes up a lot of one of our squares.In cutteslowe Park there are 6 football pitches,4 hockey pitches,4 hard tennis courts,1 putting green, 1 rugby pitch,1bowling green and one cricket pitch.There are also two playgrounds:a young children's one and an older children's one.In the young chilren's playground there is a paddling pool.Also there is a duck pond and an aviary.In the aviry there is a golden pheasant, a parakeet,a bantam, a canary,a finch,a silver pheasant,a budgerigar and a rabbit. cutteslowe park is a place for all the family.
